Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.31,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是吹不好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:35.82,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.01,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒，乃繪留？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:46.84,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,102.5)}梅雨的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:46.84,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,681.25)} 玻璃上的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.73,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶錢包了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.51,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.42,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍（身份）牌呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.05,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:51.76,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:52.39,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.05,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙巾呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:53.45,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:54.30,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:54.97,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:55.57,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指南針呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.30,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.37,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾糧呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:57.79,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:58.79,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭盔呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.54,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.54,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手槍？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.32,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.13,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手榴彈！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.17,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.30,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的，小彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.59,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀，嚇我一跳，真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.35,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來想一想，應該很快就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.14,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞心眼，梨旺前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.65,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個最近關係很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:26.06,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺就像擔心自己小孩子的媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧，這是今天的清單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:37.58,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了，今天你們的任務是進城採購這個清單上的東西。明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:38.16,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.62,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，安全駕駛，去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:46.96,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:55.10,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點回來啊，晚飯是濃湯燉牛肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.36,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘快回來喔！!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.08,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個母親一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:06.96,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次呢，乃繪留，兩個人一起進城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:07.81,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:13.07,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖這麼說，我好像是第一次進城…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.36,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！好漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.30,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 啊！那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:26.71,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和潑水祭的時候完全不一樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.36,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很平和，很安靜的小城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:41.16,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:44.86,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的那個是特洛華州獨特的屋頂裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.42,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著消災除魔的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.30,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是飲水處的模型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:55.54,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是喜碧查共和國的第12代君主阿利愷阿魯卡利亞二世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:00.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.26,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.81,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，說過了，安全駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.82,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:12.46,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪留真是什麼都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.93,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳，大小姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:23.02,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來還是不進來能不能快點決定？妨礙營業了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.08,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！潑水祭時候的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.90,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.86,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別戲弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.66,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣不會見風使舵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.99,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那至少叫我奈緒美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.41,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒美…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.46,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下次的發貨是下個月？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.31,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.91,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便問下，那孩子知道麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:03.41,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:11.12,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是軍人，一點都不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:11.73,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.10,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.65,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:21.33,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛來的時候就很在意呢，喜歡麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:30.16,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問，摸一下可以麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.52,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降A調
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.54,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是魚吧？名字是什麽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.39,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.32,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.16,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:07:00.67,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是海豚，比魚更接近我們人類的一種生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:04.10,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海裡還有生物的時候的海生哺乳類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.21,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海？在大海裡的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.42,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:10.04,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:17.76,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作那類東西很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.47,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大叔是一個和自己面相不符的羅曼蒂克主義者…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.99,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作的人你認識嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.76,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市旁邊有家大工房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.62,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡所有的玻璃工藝品都是那裡的產品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.06,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看一看啊，製作的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.02,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:35.77,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:38.26,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:47.77,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，建御雷的零件是那個玻璃工廠做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:52.25,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，奈緒美也幫忙收集著以前的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:56.93,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是乃繪留也很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.93,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼複雜的機器也漸漸修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.08,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:07.87,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記暗號喇叭的暗號代碼就已經腦袋滿滿的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:11.77,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼難吧，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:16.77,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為機器不會背叛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.21,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪留
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，找你295萬円
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:25.77,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！？那麼多？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.57,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了，應該找我2円75錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.02,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣呢，乃繪留
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:34.96,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給，找你錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:36.96,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.91,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近早上的喇叭是你吹的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.61,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.07,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還吹得很爛，不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:47.16,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，我很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.22,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，一下子就醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:03.25,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩，我要儘快吹好，不給鎮上的人們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.75,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清哉太狡猾了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:16.08,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不服氣的話來追我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.87,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方…  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.22,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.30,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.33,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶，撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.08,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:29.97,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.86,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在潑水祭見過的女孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.86,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨手笨腳的大姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.13,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.86,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體看起來已經完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.87,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個殺人犯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:58.38,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清哉，這些人和你的雙親沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.46,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一樣，軍隊什麼的最討厭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.35,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快從鎮上滾出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:06.52,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上難聽死了的喇叭聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.78,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:11.01,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，清哉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:14.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起，說了很失禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.16,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:19.04,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子是戰爭孤兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:22.06,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以看見軍人就不分好壞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.09,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪留
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:30.21,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，我們是軍人這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.49,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.61,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪留…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:53.95,Soratitleonwhite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(980,180)\frz270}天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:53.95,Soratitleonwhite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(980,300)\frz270}空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:53.95,Soratitleonwhite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(980,420)\frz270}之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:53.95,Soratitleonwhite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(980,540)\frz270}音
