Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.21,0:24:24.14,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回：
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.14,0:24:25.06,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山中漫步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:26.76,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.89,0:24:32.03,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事純屬虛構。\N與一切現實中人物，團體和事件無關
